h often ruins the atmosphere of the story and the setting, and also contains a number of mistakes throughout the book. Additionally the simplicity of the plot and the shallowness of characterisation made the quality suffer slightly. However, these are all negatives that can be easily corrected in sequels, and I’m ready to give dear Roger the benefit of doubt because of how intriguing the concept is.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eOverall, this is a very short and enjoyable introduction to one of the great fantasy series of the previous century.","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/26681101?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"fantasy","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/26681101?shelf=fantasy"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"2016","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/26681101?shelf=2016"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1025379682"},"likeCount":57,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":9,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.LiQ5sHM789bSltw29kikbg":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.LiQ5sHM789bSltw29kikbg","__typename":"Book"},"User:7298986":{"id":7298986,"__typename":"User","legacyId":7298986,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1611657221i/7298986._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":2244,"viewableName":"✘✘ Sarah ✘✘ (former Nefarious Breeder of Murderous Crustaceans)","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/7298986-sarah-former-nefarious-breeder-of-murderous-crustaceans","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":6887},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.2NV26PXc5StYVh2E5nXNYw":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.2NV26